<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>DeepSeek的战略转向：从"不融资"到"融对资" · AI深度解读</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0a0a0a;
  --surface: #111111;
  --surface-2: #1a1a1a;
  --border: #222222;
  --text: #ededed;
  --text-secondary: #888888;
  --text-muted: #555555;
  --accent: #3b82f6;
  --accent-dim: #1e3a5f;
  --blue: #58a6ff;
  --blue-soft: rgba(59,130,246,0.1);
  --green: #4ade80;
  --amber: #fbbf24;
  --rose: #fb7185;
  --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'Inter', 'PingFang SC', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', Consolas, monospace;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  line-height: 1.85;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* ===== Container ===== */
.container {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
}

/* ===== Hero ===== */
.hero {
  padding: 64px 0 40px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .hero { padding: 48px 0 32px; }
}
.hero .badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--blue);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.25;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
}
.hero h1 span { color: var(--blue); }
.hero .subtitle {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
  padding-left: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero .meta {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.hero .meta .author { color: var(--text-secondary); }

/* ===== Section ===== */
.section { padding: 28px 0 16px; }
.section .part-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.section h2 {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  color: #fff;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .section h2 { font-size: 20px; }
}
.section p {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #ccc;
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .section p { font-size: 14px; }
}
.section p strong { color: #fff; }
.section sup { color: var(--blue); font-size: 12px; }
.section sup a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }

/* ===== Info Block (时间线/公式/对比/进化) ===== */
.info-card {
  padding: 20px 16px;
  background: #0a0a0a;
}
.info-card-inner {
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 24px 20px;
  background: #1a1a1a;
}
.info-card-title {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #e0e0e0;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

/* 时间线 - 纯 flex 布局，无 absolute */
.tl-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.tl-dot-col {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  padding-top: 4px;
}
.tl-dot {
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid #888;
  background: #1a1a1a;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.tl-dot.active {
  border-color: var(--blue);
  background: var(--blue);
}
.tl-line {
  width: 2px;
  flex: 1;
  min-height: 24px;
  border-left: 2px dashed #444;
}
.tl-text {
  flex: 1;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
}
.tl-date { font-size: 11px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.tl-value { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #e0e0e0; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.tl-detail { font-size: 13px; color: #888; line-height: 1.5; }
.tl-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 6px; }
.tl-tag { padding: 2px 8px; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 10px; color: #888; }
.tl-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.tl-row:last-child .tl-line { display: none; }

/* 公式 */
.formula-flex {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.formula-block {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 14px 12px;
  border: 2px solid #333;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  min-width: 80px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.formula-block .f-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.formula-block .f-label { font-size: 11px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.formula-block .f-value { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }
.formula-block.blue { border-color: #3b82f6; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); }
.formula-block.blue .f-value { color: #3b82f6; }
.formula-block.purple { border-color: #8b5cf6; background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); }
.formula-block.purple .f-value { color: #8b5cf6; }
.formula-block.green { border-color: #10b981; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1); }
.formula-block.green .f-value { color: #10b981; }
.formula-op {
  font-size: 24px;
  color: #444;
  font-weight: 300;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.formula-eq {
  font-size: 28px;
  color: #e0e0e0;
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.formula-note {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #888;
  line-height: 1.7;
  background: #222;
}

/* 对比表 */
.compare-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #ccc;
}
.compare-table th {
  padding: 8px;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  font-weight: 700;
  background: #222;
  text-align: left;
  color: #e0e0e0;
}
.compare-table td {
  padding: 8px;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  color: #ccc;
}
.compare-table .hl { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.08); }
.compare-table .hl td:first-child { color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }
.compare-table .company-name { color: #e0e0e0; font-weight: 600; }

/* 进化组件 */
.evo-flex {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .evo-flex { flex-direction: column; }
}
.evo-box {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 16px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: #222;
  border: 1px solid #444;
}
.evo-box.new {
  border-color: var(--blue);
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.08);
}
.evo-box .evo-ver {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.evo-box.old .evo-ver { color: #666; }
.evo-box.new .evo-ver { color: var(--blue); }
.evo-box .evo-quote {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #ccc;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border-radius: 6px;
  border-left: 3px solid #555;
}
.evo-box.new .evo-quote { border-left-color: var(--blue); color: #e0e0e0; }
.evo-box .evo-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.evo-arrow {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 24px;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  padding: 0 4px;
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .evo-arrow { display: none; }
}
.evo-footnote {
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #888;
  line-height: 1.6;
  text-align: center;
  background: #222;
}

/* ===== Highlight ===== */
.highlight {
  padding: 28px 0;
}
.highlight blockquote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: var(--blue-soft);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-weight: 600;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ===== Divider ===== */
.divider {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 0;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

/* ===== Epilogue ===== */
.epilogue {
  padding: 36px 0;
}
.epilogue p {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* ===== References ===== */
.refs {
  padding: 32px 0 24px;
}
.refs h3 {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #666;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.refs p {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #555;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.refs a { color: var(--blue); }

/* ===== Footer ===== */
.footer {
  padding: 36px 0;
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.footer .brand {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.footer .slogan {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="badge">AI深度解读 · 资本分析</div>
  <h1>DeepSeek的战略转向<br><span>从"不融资"到"融对资"</span></h1>
  <div class="subtitle">500亿估值 · 梁文锋自掏200亿 · V4.1六月见 · Harness对标Claude Code</div>
  <div class="meta"><span class="author">文 / AI深度解读</span> · 2026.05.21</div>
</div>

<!-- Intro -->
<div style="padding:20px 0 12px">
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;line-height:1.9;font-style:italic">"不融资"的DeepSeek终于拿钱了，但这不是理想主义的终结，而是它的一次进化。21天估值翻5倍、创始人自掏200亿、组建Harness团队对标Claude Code——这家曾经最"离群"的中国AI公司，正在用更成熟的方式继续做AI。</p>
</div>

<!-- Part 1 -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="part-label">PART 1</div>
  <h2>那个"不融资"的传说</h2>
  <p>很长一段时间里，DeepSeek这个名字在中国AI圈的叙事里，被包裹在一层理想主义的光环中。</p>
  <p>创始人梁文锋，量化投资大佬出身，带着一群顶尖研究员，在国产大模型狂飙突进的三年里，硬是没融过一分钱。当其他几家大模型公司——智谱、MiniMax、月之暗面、百川——轮番收割资本市场的时候，DeepSeek像一座沉默的灯塔，安静地训练着模型。</p>
  <p><strong>"三不铁律"</strong>在圈内广为流传：不融资、不上市、不商业化。</p>
  <p>这不是刻意标榜。梁文锋的思路很清楚——用自有资金养一支精锐研究团队，专注把模型做深做透。融资就意味着被资本节奏绑架，而研究需要的是长期主义。</p>
  <p>但2026年5月，一切都变了。</p>
  <p>21天，估值从100亿人民币飙到500亿<sup><a href="#ref-1">[1]</a></sup>。梁文锋自己掏了200亿进来。投资方被精心挑选，不是什么热钱都收。股权结构被提前锁死，确保创始团队的控制权纹丝不动。</p>
  <p>DeepSeek拿钱了。</p>
  <p>消息一出，讨论两极分化。有人说"理想主义破灭了"，有人说"终于想通了"。</p>
  <p>但这两种说法都只说对了一半。这不是妥协，是进化。<strong>"不融资1.0"版本，正在升级为"融对资2.0"版本</strong>——一种更成熟、更负责任的技术理想主义。</p>
</div>

<!-- 配图1：融资时间线 -->
<div class="info-card">
  <div class="info-card-inner">
    <div class="info-card-title">📈 DeepSeek 融资时间线：21天估值翻5倍</div>
    <div class="tl-row">
      <div class="tl-dot-col">
